Description: 美国国务院表示，在中美两国之间局势紧张之际，美国官员在北京与中国外交官员进行了“坦诚而富有成效的沟通”。

Images: ["[2023-06-06T01...](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-06-06T011916Z_1657043405_RC2CD1A623WT_RTRMADP_3_CHINA-USA-DIPLOMACY-1686017180-1686024120.jpg)", "[image-3-16860...](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-3-1686024252.jpg)", "[image-4-16860...](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-4-1686023924.jpg)"]

